      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the cauliflower has started to brown, add the<strong> ginger & garlic paste</strong>,<strong> ground turmeric </strong>and <strong>curry powder </strong>and cook for 1-2 min further until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
