    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain and rinse the <strong>green lentils</strong></p><p>Put the <strong>wholemeal pittas </strong>in the <strong>toaster </strong>for 1-2 min or until warmed through</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
